### Task: MIITAS API — Auth (Google + session)
### Base URL matches PORT in .env (default here: 3008). JWT audience/issuer must match host:port.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3008/api/v1
@accessToken = YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_AFTER_GOOGLE_LOGIN
@refreshToken = YOUR_REFRESH_TOKEN

### Sign in with Google (exchange Google ID token for app tokens)
# @name googleAuth
POST http://localhost:3008/api/v1/auth/google
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "YOUR_GOOGLE_ID_TOKEN"
}

### Refresh access + refresh tokens
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

### Logout (invalidates session / blacklists tokens)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
